						               													<description>There is a country in a different world where the existence of a &amp;quot;devil&amp;quot; is believed and the leaders of each party gather to hold an &amp;quot;election campaign&amp;quot; to determine the next leader.&amp;#10;The &amp;quot;election campaign&amp;quot; is a 4-week competition in which the party leaders themselves show off their different strengths to determine who is most suitable for the next leader.&amp;#10;However, strength alone will not bring people together. Every week you have to make a new pledge and deliver on it.&amp;#10;At times, it may be necessary to use the forbidden &amp;quot;devil's power&amp;quot;. Who will gain the most support from the public and become the next leader?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#229;&amp;#155;&amp;#189;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#174;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#159;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#129;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#171;&amp;#230;&amp;#130;&amp;#170;&amp;#233;&amp;#173;&amp;#148;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#168;&amp;#229;&amp;#165;&amp;#145;&amp;#231;&amp;#180;&amp;#132;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#151;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#159;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#137;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#136;&amp;#227;&amp;#130;&amp;#137;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#132;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#147;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#168;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#171;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#170;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#163;&amp;#227;&amp;#129;&amp;#159;!! (I made a contract with the devil for the sake of my country, and it turned out to be a big deal!!) is a must follow trick-taker with 3 main suits (financial power, armed power, and intelligence), 1 devil suit, and 1 priest suit. The devil and priest suits can be played at anytime regardless of the must follow rule. The winner is the highest of the lead suit unless a devil suit is played, then the highest devil suit wins. However, if a priest card is played in the same trick as a devil card, then the priest card will win. The winner will gain a crystal. Players are attempting to complete contracts they took at the beginning of the round. You will score based on how well did on your contract. The player most points when one of the end game conditions are triggered wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
